  59:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****             __HAL_UART_ENABLE_IT() and __HAL_UART_DISABLE_IT() inside the transmit
  60:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****             and receive process.
