 286:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****       (+) For the asynchronous mode only these parameters can be configured:
 287:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Baud Rate
